# Playwright

Playwright is a cross-browser automation framework by Microsoft that enables reliable end-to-end testing across Chromium, Firefox, and Safari with modern web features.

## Key Features

- **Cross-browser testing** - Chromium, Firefox, Safari support
- **Auto-waiting** - Smart element detection and waiting
- **Mobile emulation** - Test responsive designs
- **Network interception** - Mock APIs and monitor requests
- **Screenshot testing** - Visual regression validation
- **Parallel execution** - Fast test runs across browsers
- **Trace viewer** - Debug with timeline and screenshots

## Use Cases

- End-to-end testing
- Cross-browser validation
- Mobile web testing
- Visual regression testing
- API testing integration

## Get Started with Playwright

Reliable cross-browser testing for modern web apps. Visit [playwright.dev](https://playwright.dev) to implement comprehensive browser automation.